Notice all the locks attached to the railing. Couples do this ritual to symbolize their forever lasting love. Their key is then thrown in the seine river.
Come with your best gal, buy a lock from one of the guys selling them, write your names on it, lock it to the bridge, and chuck the keys in the river.
